{"ID":"20260305082130-8gnt8ne","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-8gnt8ne","title":"纯虚函数和抽象类","type":"doc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082201-lmycyvy","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082201-lmycyvy"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eWFtbA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"---\ntitle: 纯虚函数和抽象类\ndate created: 星期一, 十月 20日 2025, 11:32:26 中午\ndate modified: 星期二, 十月 21日 2025, 1:39:02 下午\n---"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-84oa0nn","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-84oa0nn","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"纯虚函数与抽象类"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-49g3qtp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-49g3qtp","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"定义："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-h1bj1fh","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-h1bj1fh","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-x664iv0","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-x664iv0","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-yirqt83","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-yirqt83","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"纯虚函数没有函数体，其函数体应该在派生类中给出。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-71yf1sm","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-71yf1sm","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-qw74gpx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-qw74gpx","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"含有纯虚函数的类被称为抽象类，抽象类不能有具体的对象。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-5rp6l4p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-5rp6l4p","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果一个类定义了纯虚函数，即使在类外给出纯虚函数的定义，这个类也是抽象类。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"若抽象类的派生类\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e没有重新定义该类的纯虚函数\u003c/font\u003e，或者\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e定义了新的纯虚函数\u003c/font\u003e，那么该派生类也是一个抽象类。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在多级派生的过程中，如果到某个派生类为止，所有纯虚函数都已在派生类中全部重新定义了函数体，则该派生类就会成为具体类。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-59k84zw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-59k84zw","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"设计抽象类的目的："},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"建立一个公有的接口，动态的使用它的成员函数。"}]}]}